https://www.loc.gov/resource/sn84037548/1957-11-28/ed-1/?fo=json&sp=3", "of": 4, "page_list": [{"number": 1, "url": "https://www.loc.gov/resource/sn84037548/1957-11-28/ed-1/?fo=json&sp=1"}, {"number": 2, "url": null}, {"number": 3, "url": "https://www.loc.gov/resource/sn84037548/1957-11-28/ed-1/?fo=json&sp=3"}, {"number": 4, "url": "https://www.loc.gov/resource/sn84037548/1957-11-28/ed-1/?fo=json&sp=4"}], "perpage": 1, "perpage_options": [25, 50, 100, 150], "previous": "https://www.loc.gov/resource/sn84037548/1957-11-28/ed-1/?fo=json&sp=1", "results": "2 - 2", "to": 2, "total": 4}, "previous_resource": {"label": "Previous Issue", "url": "https://www.loc.gov/resource/sn84037548/1957-11-26/ed-1/?fo=json&sp=1"}, "related_items": [{"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://lccn.loc.gov/74696186", "http://www.loc.gov/item/74696186/", "https://search.catalog.loc.gov/instances/243b586f-27f3-5101-b5ff-bbb4076bde05", "https://hdl.loc.gov/loc.gmd/g5012s.ct000319", "http://www.loc.gov/resource/g5012s.ct000319/"], "campaigns": [], "contributor": ["lode, o. h. de", "beck, i. m."], "date": "1754", "dates": ["1754"], "description": ["Hand colored. Cadastral map showing land ownership. \"Tilegned deres h\u00f6y grevelige excellence her Adam Gotlob Moltke.\" Includes listing of windmills by quarter and insets \"Tegning til byen Friderichsst\u00e6d\" and \"Tegning over byen Christianst\u00e6d paa eylandet St. Croix, faavit den allerede er bebygt.\" Scale ca. 1:60,000. LC Luso-Hispanic World, 980 Available also through the Library of Congress Web site as a raster image. LC copy annotated in pen-and-ink to show land owners in 1767. Vault AACR2: 650/1; 651/2; 650/3; 651/4"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-04-29T15:39:14.781Z", "group": ["gmd.mar", "catalog-split-15", "catalog", "general-maps", "main-catalog-split-15"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/74696186/", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/storage-services/service/gmd/gmd5/g5012/g5012s/ct000